bio: Hi,This is Rocky.I am from Bangladesh & I am a freelancer.
impactDescription: We provided over 100 OP News updates to our audience of 2,000 podcast listeners and 230 newsletter subscribers. In the fast-changing Optimism Collective, we play a crucial role in keeping users well-informed. OP News is a series of Optimism-related updates featured within our Ethereum News flash briefing in a dedicated segment called Optimism Highlights.
